---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About">
  <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">About Nibble Labs</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
    Nibble Labs is a software studio focused on building and testing small, well-defined solutions to everyday operational problems. We work in short cycles — identify friction, automate what matters, and validate ideas through real-world use.
  </p>

  <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold mb-3">What We Do</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-8">
    <li>Lightweight workflow and reporting automation</li>
    <li>Data cleanup, integration, and transformation</li>
    <li>Rapid pilots to validate software ideas</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold mb-3">The Blog</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
    The blog is where we write about the ideas that shape how we build software — continuous delivery, lean thinking, domain-driven design, and the craft of sustainable engineering.
  </p>
</Base>
